{
  "stem": "21731.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they started-- a thousand people had to be brought to a certain place for hard work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And those people disappeared then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then they wanted this and they wanted that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one day, when the Judenrat could not [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] give them what they asked-- I can't remember what it was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Perhaps I never knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They just killed the three most important of the Judenrat and hanged them on the Platz [NON-ENGLISH], the middle of Lwow, on a balcony.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they were hanging there for a few days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Amongst them was my uncle, a lawyer, Josef Parnas.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then one day I came back from the hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there was my mother and Jan sitting on the stairs-- my mother with two suitcases or boxes or whatever it was, Jan with the, the cage with the canary-- waiting for me.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were thrown out of there-- all Jews out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they waited for me, even not knowing whether I will come back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could have been caught in the meantime somewhere on the street and not come back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kreisberg was in the ghetto already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I told before, he was a wealthy man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He, I think, that-- what I was told later-- he gave to the Judenrat a lot of not only money, but gold, jewelry, in case they will be caught.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so they can bribe the Gestapo or whoever caught them, or if he needs some money.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because naturally, he couldn't have gold with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Judenrat always was able to provide him whatever he needed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he got two rooms in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he got a little room for my mother and Jan and me there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
